      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Great interest has been aroused\namong men active in the cause Of\nunion labor by the series Of articles\npublished In The Press, written by\nDana sIeeth, relative to tho united\nefforts Of employers In tho coast\ncities for open shop towns.\n\n\nWhat Mr.. Sleeth has told Of the\nfight has been known In an indirect\nway, but the details and extent Of\nthe plot to down labor was not as\nfully known until The Press laid\nthe matter bare.\n\n\nIf ever the Citizens alliance un-\ndertakes to make fight on organ\nlied labor In Spokane it will find\nthe workers Of the city united to a\nman. Organized labor may divide"
